      <div data-hook="genome-widget" class="a-row a-spacing-mini"><div class="a-profile" data-a-size="small"><div aria-hidden="true" class="a-profile-avatar-wrapper"><div class="a-profile-avatar"><img src="./product-8-c_files/grey-pixel.gif" class="a-lazy-loaded" data-src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default.png"><noscript><img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default.png"/></noscript></div></div><div class="a-profile-content"><span class="a-profile-name">NikonBuff</span></div></div></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-none"><h5><i data-hook="cmps-review-star-rating" class="a-icon a-icon-star a-star-5 review-rating"><span class="a-icon-alt">5.0 out of 5 stars</span></i><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span data-hook="review-title" class="a-size-base review-title a-color-base review-title-content a-text-bold">







  
  
    <span>Not expensive, easy to install device.</span>
  
</span></h5></div><span data-hook="review-date" aria-level="6" class="a-size-base a-color-secondary review-date" role="heading">Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 7 June 2021</span><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini review-data review-format-strip"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-color-secondary">Colour Name: C-black</span><i aria-hidden="true" class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i><a aria-label="Verified Purchase: Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon" class="a-link-normal" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.amazon.ie/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_avp?nodeId=G8UYX7LALQC8V9KA"><span data-hook="avp-badge" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Verified Purchase</span></a></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data"><span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text"><div data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container review-text-read-more-expander" style="max-height:300px"><div data-hook="review-collapsed" data-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">







  
  
    <span>Nice little device. Installed in the spare loo where I did not want to spend on an electric unit. Very thin so feels easy to break but as long as not mishandled it should hold for fair usage. We did not have hot water supply or electricity connection so this was the best possible option. Was easy enough to fit with right tools, took some time for me as I am poor at DIY and our cistern started leaking after I fitted this but fixed by tightening a few parts.<br>As other reviewers have mentioned there is a hole below the control unit and not sure why it is there but mine is not leaking yet.<br>Usage wise works well for summer but will be good to see how usable it will be for winter with only cold water supply. Would have been good to have:<br>1) jet position adjustment for posterior mode.<br>2) auto off would have helped specially for the self cleaning mode as it is easy to be forgotten in on mode.<br></span>
  
</div><div class="a-expander-header a-expander-partial-collapse-header" style="opacity: 0; display: none;"><div class="a-expander-content-fade"></div><a href="javascript:void(0)" data-hook="expand-collapse-read-more-less" aria-label="Read more of this review" aria-expanded="false" role="button" data-action="a-expander-toggle" class="a-declarative" data-a-expander-toggle="{&quot;allowLinkDefault&quot;:true, &quot;expand_prompt&quot;:&quot;Read more&quot;, &quot;collapse_prompt&quot;:&quot;Read less&quot;}"><i class="a-icon a-icon-extender-expand"></i><span class="a-expander-prompt">Read more</span></a></div></div></span></div><div class="a-row cr-vote-action-bar"><span class="cr-vote" data-hook="review-voting-widget">
