    <span>So far, clean tooshies and dry feet.<br>Feels nicely made, install is very easy (Flexibility and grip strength dependant) and components feel solid- No leaks or drips so far.<br>Function- A jet for the rusty sherifs badge, another for the wizards sleeve and a dial to adjust strength. All intuitive and work well. Buttons slightly jiggly, but so are the best of us. Will buy again for our other two toilets.<br></span>
  
